==Creation==
To create supercompost, players must place 15 suitable produce (see list below) into any of the [[compost bin]]s that are located next to the [[allotment]] [[Farming/Patch locations|patches]] found around [[Gielinor]]. Once the bin is full, the lid of the compost bin must be closed to allow the contents to rot. This process takes approximately 90 minutes until completion, after which the player may open the compost bin and extract all of the supercompost by clicking on the bin or using [[bucket]]s on it. Each bucket of supercompost collected grants the player 8.5 Farming [[experience]].

Players may also use a [[compost potion]] to create supercompost. One dose of compost potion will change an entire finished bin of compost into supercompost, or one bucket of compost that has already been collected.

Supercompost can be purchased with reward points from the [[Tithe Farm]] minigame, for 5 points each.

The [[Lunar spells|Lunar spell]] [[Fertile Soil]] can be used on a patch to apply the effect of supercompost to it without using any supercompost.

